                        <div class="price-tag mb-3">₱ 1,000</div>
                        <p class="text-muted mb-4">Perfect for maintaining your pet's cleanliness between full grooms</p>
                        <ul class="list-unstyled mb-4">
                            <li class="pricing-feature"><i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success me-2"></i>Basic wash & dry</li>
